title: 2015–16 Swazi Premier League
text: The 2015–16 <a href="Swazi%20Premier%20League">Swazi Premier League</a> season was the 2015–16 season of the top level of <a href="association%20football">football</a> competition in <a href="Swaziland">Swaziland</a>. It began on 22 August 2015 and concluded on 15 May 2016.
